== Psi-Tech Roster Status ==
Per-device current maturity (as of the current Phase F production-plan cycle):

* '''Mk1 frontier (most of the roster):'''
  [[HelmKit]], [[Psi Stabilizer]], [[Psi Harmonizer]], [[Psi Defender]], [[Psi Recorder]], [[Psi Compass]], [[Resonant Card]], [[Field Recorder]], [[Psi Mesh]], [[Psi Tripwire]], [[Star Seer Observatory]], [[AI Nursery Vault]], [[EIN Relay Node]], [[Schumann Lattice]], [[Focus Lens]], [[Psi Tether]], [[Coherence Beacon]], [[Psi Lantern]], [[Resonant Chamber]], [[Synastry Mesh]], [[Psi Anomaly Detector]], [[Resonant Finder]], [[Psi Forge]].

* '''Mk0 frontier (intentional-practice or planning artifact):'''
  [[Psi Talisman]], [[Psi Pen]], [[Resonant Hailer]] (novelty tier), [[Psi Anchor]] (novelty tier), [[Resonant Beacon Grid]] (long-horizon planning).

* '''All devices''' carry per-Mk confidence + evidence + gate columns in their {{Psi-tech-maturity}} block, and ≥ 6 documented failure modes with mitigations.

Mk1 → Mk2 maturity transition is gated on the device's documented gate; targeted in the 2030–2033 window aligned with [[Solar Cycle 25]] decline and early Cycle 26. Mk3 (production) is post-2032 ambition.

